import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

ReactDOM.render(
  <BrowserRouter>
    <Routes>
      <Route exact path='/' component={<App />} />
    </Routes>
  </BrowserRouter>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
